gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 117, Magic 102
gameRecap.excerpt: Dallas defeats Orlando, 117-102. Luka Doncic led the Mavericks with 29 points, six assists, and three rebounds as Kyrie Irving (21 points, 10 assists, six rebounds) and Tim Hardaway Jr. (21 points) totaled 42 points. Paolo Banchero led Orlando with 22 points, six assists, and five rebounds while Cole Anthony added 19 points and five assists. Dallas improves to 6-1 as Orlando moves to 4-3.
